{
  "stem": "1062.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We, the Jewish people, were a little bit happy because in Romania, things were getting hot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "The iron guard in the, in the government were blaming the Jews for the province of-- for losing the province of Bessarabia.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "So we thought that we're going to be rescued by the Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Hungarians came in in 1940, and we were part of Hungary.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, I didn't speak no Hungarian then, but they sent-- they send a teacher to the-- a Hungarian teacher to my school, and you know, I, I started to learn the language.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Romanian population in Comlausa, my village, were also oppressed because the Hungarian used to take them for forced labor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they hated the Romanians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then the war broke out with Russia in-- with the Soviet Union between Germany and, and the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was in 1941, in June.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The end of 1941, Hungary declared war on the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PHONE RINGING] And they went ahead, and they took all the Jewish men, and they, and they were conscripted into the army.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PHONE RINGING] And-- [PHONE RINGING] --they were conscripted into the army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not into the army, into a work battalion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PHONE RINGING] Into work-- they were-- they were-- they were called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] And my father was taken into the work, work battalion.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was in 1942.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was like in February 1942.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, anyway, my father was taken in by the Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was taken into the-- not into a work battalion, what's called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All the Jewish men were taken into, into those work battalions.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were-- they had a yellow armband on their, on their, on their sleeves.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they would do mostly work, all kinds of work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then he was shipped out to the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
